    "description": "CRI Middleware Co., Ltd. provides audio and video-related middleware solutions in Japan. It operates through the Gaming and Enterprise segments. The company offers audio and video-related middleware solutions for game development, as well as image optimization solutions and audio production services. It also involved in the research and development of audio and video solutions, licensing and support of middleware, and related software development subcontracting activities; and sound production, CD pressing and manufacturing, studio management, and event planning business. In addition, the company offers CRIWARE License and technical support services. The company serves the video gaming, enterprise, mobility, audio/karaoke, web services/e-commerce, online communication, embedded systems, and other fields under the CRIWARE and OPTPiX brand names. CRI Middleware Co., Ltd. was founded in 1983 and is headquartered in Shibuya, Japan."
